YP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/27286/', '', 'Dextromethorphan, Clofedanol, Benzonatate, Pentoxyverine, Codeine', 'Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Tepotinib, Avapritinib, Bosutinib, Lapatinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, Cobimetinib, Capmatinib, Ibrutinib, More', 1767369485);
